==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tarsal
<hw>Tar"sal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Of
or pertaining to the tarsus (either of the foot or eye).</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A tarsal bone or cartilage; a
tarsale.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Tarsal tetter</b></col> <fld>(Med.)</fld>, <cd>an
eruptive disease of the edges of the eyelids; a kind of
bleareye.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tarsal</ent>⟦br⟧

